(1712, 536, 'home_page_copy_paragraphs_0_home_page_copy_paragraph', 'Stone built, Trevyr Barn has been restored using traditional materials including stone and oak floors and wooden beams. It is furnished in a comfortable contemporary style to create the perfect holiday accommodation for a short break or longer stay.'),
