(1714, 536, 'home_page_copy_paragraphs_1_home_page_copy_paragraph', 'Located between the Wye Valley AONB and the Black Mountains, just to the east of the Brecon Beacons National Park, Trevyr Barn is an excellent base for exploring this beautiful and historic area.'),
