(24, 1, '2016-11-13 12:34:41', '2016-11-13 12:34:41', '<div class="row">\n<div class="box">\n<div class="col-sm-12">\n<h2 class="brand-before text-center"><small>Welcome to</small></h2>\n<h1 class="brand-name text-center">brand_name</h1>\n\n<hr class="tagline-divider" />\n\n<ul class="pull-right highlights">\n 	<li>Visit Wales 5 Star ratingx</li>\n 	<li>Green Tourism Business Scheme Gold Rating</li>\n 	<li>Luxury accommodation for 6 - plus 2 folding beds</li>\n 	<li>Spacious farmhouse kitchen/dining room</li>\n 	<li>Large sitting room with wood burning stove</li>\n 	<li>Views over unspoilt pastures and woodland</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr class="visible-xs" />\n\nStone built, Trevyr Barn has been restored using traditional materials including stone and oak floors and wooden beams. It is furnished in a comfortable contemporary style to create the perfect holiday accommodation for a short break or longer stay.\n\nLocated between the Wye Valley AONB and the Black Mountains, just to the east of the Brecon Beacons National Park, Trevyr Barn is an excellent base for exploring this beautiful and historic area.\n\nThis fascinating region of the Welsh borders offers plenty of outdoor activities for all ages and abilities, interesting historical sites and is renowned for its excellent local produce and restaurants.\n\n</div>\n\n<div class="col-sm-12">\n\n<a href="http://www.grosmont.org/">Grosmont</a> is within easy driving distance of London, Cardiff, the Midlands and Manchester. It is well serviced by local and national train services via Abergavenny, Hereford and Newport (London-Swansea main line).\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Home page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-11-13 12:34:41', '2016-11-13 12:34:41', '', 7, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/7-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
