election of local produce" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-8">\r\n<h2>Food shopping</h2>\r\nMonmouth is justly proud of the fantastic food and drink produced locally. We hope that our visitors will enjoy sampling what''s on offer. The <a title="Made in Monmouthshire" href="http://www.madeinmonmouthshire.com" target="_blank">Made in Monmouthshire</a> website provides plenty of information about local producers of food, drink, arts and crafts.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Food, Drink & Dining Guide', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '78-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-22 08:01:26', '2016-04-22 08:01:26', '', 78, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/78-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
