fantastic food and drink produced locally. We hope that our visitors will enjoy sampling what''s on offer.  The <a href="http://www.madeinmonmouthshire.com" target="_blank" title="Made in Monmouthshire">Made in Monmouthshire</a> website provides plenty of information about local producers of food, drink, arts and crafts.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>', 'Food, Drink & Dining Guide', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '78-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-22 08:04:59', '2016-04-22 08:04:59', '', 78, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/78-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
