(147, 1, '2016-04-22 10:31:01', '2016-04-22 10:31:01', '  <div class="row">\r\n    <div class="box">\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n        <h1 class="brand-name text-center">How to contact us</h1>\r\n        <hr />\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class="row">\r\n    <div class="box">\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-8">\r\n        <p>To check availability and prices please contact Louise and Alex.</p>\r\n        <p>Email: <strong>louise@trevyrbarn.co.uk</strong></p>\r\n        <p>Phone: <a href="tel:07786 243355"> 07786 243355</a></p>\r\n        <p>Whether you email or leave a message, please state your preferred dates and any alternative dates that you may be considering so that we can come back to you with all the information that you require.</p>\r\n        <p>We look forward to meeting you.</p>\r\n        <p><strong>Louise & Alex</strong></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-4">\r\n        <p>To check availability and prices please contact Louise and Alex.</p>\r\n        <p>Email: <strong>louise@trevyrbarn.co.uk</strong></p>\r\n        <p>Phone: <a href="tel:07786 243355"> 07786 243355</a></p>\r\n        <p>Whether you email or leave a message, please state your preferred dates and any alternative dates that you may be considering so that we can come back to you with all the information that you require.</p>\r\n        <p>We look forward to meeting you.</p>\r\n        <p><strong>Louise & Alex</strong></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class="row">\r\n    <div class="box">\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n        <h2>From our guest book</h2>\r\n        <img class="img-responsive img-border pull-right" src="img/spring.jpg" alt="Spring at Trevyr Barn">\r\n        <blockquote>\r\n          <p>"...after just a couple of days it felt like home. We can''t wait to come back."</p>\r\n          <footer><cite>Pat & Barry, Macclesfield.</cite></footer>\r\n        </blockquote>\r\n        <blockquot