(408, 1, '2016-10-27 16:03:26', '2016-10-27 16:03:26', '<div class="row">\n    <div class="box">\n      <div class="col-sm-12">\n        <h1 class="brand-name text-center">Outside</h1>\n        <hr />\n      </div>\n            <div class="col-sm-4"> <img class="img-responsive img-border img-left" src="[insert_php] bloginfo(''stylesheet_directory''); [/insert_php]/images/trevyrbarn01.jpg" alt="The garden"> \n</div>\n<div class="col-sm-8">\n        <h2>Garden</h2>\n        <p>Trevyr Barn has a private courtyard with barbeque, as well as a lawned garden looking out onto the orchard.</p>\n        <p>We have 10 acres of fields, an orchard and a brook. Our guests are welcome to explore, and help themselves to fruit when in season (apples, cherries, pears, plums and blackberries). We have a wealth of wildlife to enjoy and have bird and bat boxes in the orchard to encourage them. Our night skies are pitch black and perfect for star gazing.</p>\n        <p>There is parking on the property for two cars and secure storage for bicycles and other outdoor equipment.</p>\n      </div>      \n      \n    </div>\n', 'Outside', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '70-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-10-27 16:03:26', '2016-10-27 16:03:26', '', 70, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/70-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
