.jpg" alt="Trevyr Barn, bedroom"> </div>\r\n            <div class="item"> <img class="img-responsive img-full" src="img/Trevyrbarn_080711_0108.jpg" alt="Trevyr Barn, double bedroom"> </div>\r\n            <div class="item"> <img class="img-responsive img-full" src="img/Trevyrbarn_080711_0125.jpg" alt="Trevyr Barn, bathroom"> </div>\r\n            <!--<div class="item"> <img class="img-responsive img-full" src="img/Trevyrbarn_080711_0156.jpg" alt="Trevyr Barn, garden"> </div>-->\r\n            <div class="item"> <img class="img-responsive img-full" src="img/trevyr_092203_0087.jpg" alt="Grosmont, local sign"> </div>\r\n            <div class="item"> <img class="img-responsive img-full" src="img/Trevyrbarn_080711_0184.jpg" alt="Trevyr Barn, outside sitting space"> </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          \r\n          <!-- Controls --> \r\n          <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide="prev"> <span class="icon-prev"></span> </a> <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide="next"> <span class="icon-next"></span> </a> </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>', 'Gallery', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '163-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-15 15:04:20', '2016-10-15 15:04:20', '', 163, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/163-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(190, 1, '2016-10-15 15:06:11', '2016-10-15 15:06:11', ' <div class="row">\r\n    <div class="box">\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n        <h1 class="brand-name text-center">The practicalities</h1>\r\n        <hr />\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class="row">\r\n    <div class="box">\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n        <h2>Location & Travel</h2>\r\n        <div id="map_canvas" class="pull-right"></div>\r\n        <p><a href="http://www.grosmont.org" target="_blank">Grosmont</a> is within easy driving distance of London, Cardiff, the Midlands and Manchester. It is well serviced by local and national train services via Abergavenny, Hereford and Newport (London-Swansea main line). A <a href="http://www.traintaxi.co.uk/" target="_blank">taxi</a> from Abergavenny station costs &pound;30 - &pound;35.</p>\r\n        <p>Public transport facilities in and around Grosmont are fairly limited; information can be found <a href="http://www.traveline-cymru.info" target="_blank" title="Traveline">here</a></p>\r\n        <p>Trevyr Barn is located just over a mile to the south west of Grosmont, We will be pleased to provide full travel information and directions upon booking.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class="row">\r\n    <div class="box">\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n        <h2>Welcome pack</h2>\r\n        <p>We include a welcome pack containing locally produced goodies\r\n        . A basket of logs is also provided.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class="row">\r\n    <div class="box">\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n        <h2>Pets</h2>\r\n        <p>We are sorry, but we are unable to accommodate pets due to livestock on neighbouring fields.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class="row">\r\n    <div class="box">\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n        <h2>Linen and towels</h2>\r\n        <p>Quality bed linen and towels are included.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class="row">\r\n    <div class="box">\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n        <h2>Parking</h2>\r\n        <p>There is parking for two cars on a gravel area directly outside the\r\n          barn, next to the lawned garden, and secure storage for bicycles.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class="row">\r\n    <div class="box">\r\n      <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n        <h2>Smoking</h2>\r\n        <p>We have a no smoking policy inside the barn.</p>\r\n        <ul class="summary visible-xs text-left">\r\n          <li>Master, double and twin bedrooms</li>\r\n          <li>Family bathroom, separate shower room downstairs</li>\r\n          <li>Views over unspoilt pastures and woodland</li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>', 'The practicalities', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '39-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-15 15:06:11', '2016-10-15 15:06:11', '', 39, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/39-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(194, 1, '2016-10-15 15:13:01', '2016-10-15 15:13:01', '<a href="http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/pricelist.pdf">pricelist</a><div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-sm-12">\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<h1 class="brand-name text-center">Booking &amp; availability</h1>\r\n<hr />\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<h2>Prices and availability</h2>\r\n<p>\r\nTrevyr Barn is available all year round. Prices vary according to the season from £475 to £900 per week. We are also happy to take bookings for short breaks and long weekends. <a href="http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/termsandconditions.pdf">Click here</a> to download details of prices and availability.</p>\r\n<p>Changeover day is usually Friday but we can be flexible outside peak times; call or email to check.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<h2>Deposits</h2>\r\nA booking deposit of 25% will be required to secure your dates, with final payment six weeks prior to arrival.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<h2>Booking</h2>\r\nTo make a booking, please contact Louise and Alex. Our\r\ndetails are on the <a href="contact.html">contact page LINK TO FIX</a>.\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box">\r\n<h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>\r\nClick <a title="terms and conditions" href="http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/pricelist.pdf">here</a> for our booking terms and conditions.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Booking and availability', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '97-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-15 15:13:01', '2016-10-15 15:13:01', '', 97, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/97-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(193, 1, '2016-10-15 15:11:40', '2016-10-15 15:11:40', '<div class="row">\r\n  <div class="box">\r\n    <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n      <h1 class="brand-name text-center">Booking & availability</h1>\r\n      <hr />\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n  <div class="box">\r\n    <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n      <h2>Prices and availability</h2>\r\n      <p> Trevyr Barn is available all year round. Prices vary according to the\r\n        season from £475 to £950 per week. We are also happy to take\r\n        bookings for short breaks and long weekends. Click <a href="docs/pricelist.pdf" title="pricelist" target="_blank">here</a> for details of prices and availability.</p>\r\n      <p>Changeover day is usually Friday but we can be flexible outside peak times; call or email to check.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n  <div class="box">\r\n    <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n      <h2>Deposits</h2>\r\n      <p>A booking deposit of 25% will be required to secure your dates, with final payment six weeks prior to arrival.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n  <div class="box">\r\n    <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n      <h2>Booking and contact</h2>\r\n      <p>To check availability and prices please contact Louise and Alex.</p>\r\n      <p>Email: <strong>louise@trevyrbarn.co.uk</strong></p>\r\n      <p>Phone: <a href="tel:07786 243355"> 07786 243355</a></p>\r\n      <p>Whether you email or leave a message, please state your preferred dates and any alternative dates that you may be considering so that we can come back to you with all the information that you require.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n  <div class="box">\r\n    <div class="col-sm-12">\r\n      <h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>\r\n      <p>Click <a href="docs/termsandconditions.pdf" target="_blank" title="terms and conditions">here</a> for our booking terms and conditions.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\