(502, 1, '2016-11-12 16:54:54', '2016-11-12 16:54:54', 'You can choose a variety of footpaths from right outside the front door\r\n(OS Landranger 161, Explorer OL13). We have a range of books, maps and leaflets to help you plan. Check out these village walks.\r\nTwenty minutes in the car puts you in the Wye Valley or the Black Mountains, a little further and you are in the heart of the Brecon Beacons. Local walking routes include: Offa’s Dyke, Wye Valley Walk, Monnow Valley Walk, Marches Way and the Three Castles Walk.', 'WALKING, HIKING AND RUNNING', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'walking-hiking-and-running', '', '', '2016-11-12 16:57:31', '2016-11-12 16:57:31', '', 0, 'http://localhost:81/wordpress-trevrybarn/?post_type=section&#038;p=502', 0, 'section', '', 0),
